work agent's actual data fields ŌĆö read those from each work agent.py's
instruction= and from its tool signatures.

### How to enable and read the logs

```bash
# Enable shadow mode
export PLANNER_SHADOW_ENABLED=1

# Grep for mismatches only
grep "\[SHADOW MISMATCH\]" your-app.log

# Grep for all shadow output
grep "\[SHADOW" your-app.log
```

