| Aspect | Home (epm-chatbot) | Work |
|---|---|---|
| Operational agents | vesting_agent, grant_agent, participant_agent | release_agent, operational_agent, participant_agent |
| `route_query` caller | ADK LLM via ToolContext | REST handler calls it directly |
| Context input | `tool_context.state` (ADK session) | Work session dict / context object |
